{"tid":1321473,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【黑色一毛預警】請負評並不要推有關「我個FD話」及招安等洗地黑警文","createTime":"2019-07-15T16:25:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T12:23:44.000Z","uid":58841,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f67a8e437ca31b86476102585f7db1d572b46365","tid":1321473,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:25:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1314078/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1314078/page/1</a><br />\n琴日成堆黑警同藍絲開post洗白都無人發現<br />\n<br />\n例子 入面有圖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1317794\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1317794</a><br />\n覺得黑警會回頭是岸班撚樣係想逆風定天真得濟<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n洗左一陣發現呢班人既招數成個月都無變過<br />\n不過我諗到而家仲會中計既人只會越黎越少<br />\n<br />\n1.留意文字口吻<br />\n-打字唔知點解又口語又書面語<br />\n-5P字<br />\n-表情撚<br />\n-表面上扮到好中立 其實仔細睇垃圾LOGIC<br />\n2.起底 最好逐個逐個POST咁望<br />\n3.唔好睇正負評數<br />\n唔知點解個篇我個FD話篇野成7000幾個負皮<br />\n千祈唔好睇正負評做人 如果唔係一定含得撚<br />\n連登羊群好撚勁<br />\n4.列入追蹤名單 知己知彼百戰百勝<br />\n5.睇推POST時間 注意五毛搞事起風<br />\n6.間中望下留COMMENT既ID<br />\n<br />\n我就黎整個五毛全攻略<br />\n你地再亂鳩開/推POST只會令我做到更多分析<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0a59cfc82dac1c0121bca68b93f5ca07eb0d985","tid":1321473,"uid":218575,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:27:22.000Z","msg":"推呀屌 <br />\n見到成班連登仔走去同5毛嘈<br />\n間接幫佢地推post <br />\n提撚咗幾十萬次<br />\n都無人理 提到燥"},{"pid":"5fcb68a35f72361c95d4f61f48203182da5590eb","tid":1321473,"uid":263423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:27:34.000Z","msg":"竟然，我仲以為有啲曲緊"},{"pid":"291502a68d0d813ff106f0baba0c1c489252ec11","tid":1321473,"uid":264811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:27:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7f02619cb0bacf1a2f952ab5cdec17c8f54bf9d","tid":1321473,"uid":588