:35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5fcb68a35f72361c95d4f61f48203182da5590eb","tid":1321473,"uid":263423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:27:34.000Z","msg":"竟然，我仲以為有啲曲緊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:41:27.000Z","msg":"呢個時勢曲都唔好亂玩"},{"pid":"1eaed5e6965e434e782980ed53f6d17cb0df4d5a","tid":1321473,"uid":264788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5fcb68a35f72361c95d4f61f48203182da5590eb","tid":1321473,"uid":263423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:27:34.000Z","msg":"竟然，我仲以為有啲曲緊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:45:07.000Z","msg":"我都係，對唔住大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ed1bf5fa513b182ba2b597315f7211226fed1f0","tid":1321473,"uid":264788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:45:19.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75eaf47b415104a0abb5a9349ff0d70be89e7734","tid":1321473,"uid":159913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:47:09.000Z","msg":"到今時今日仲有一批連登仔會幫手留言推五毛post，好戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66ee002d09cd97e9cc3c8393b7022dfb6924e2ab","tid":1321473,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:54:54.000Z","msg":"7.提防五毛開支線叫人係黑警身上轉移視線<br />\n如果唔小心轉移左佢地下一招就係正反兩邊都實行自編自導自演<br />\n例如我3日前打既呢篇野<br />\n<em><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1310215/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1310215/page/1</a><br />\n中聯辦一早出左手 某個時間段大量連儂牆post上哂去</em><br />\n目前主線只有政府 黑警 其次先到TVB<br />\n8.諷刺<br />\n你無睇錯 五毛係好鐘意玩諷刺<br />\n仲要係有骨個隻 對付呢類要用下腦"},{"pid":"2dc18c2b4471f99c181ebe735541233c3acd094e","tid":1321473,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:59:13.000Z","msg":"例子2:無證實來源，「聽人講」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1321516/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1321516/page/1</a><br />\n呢類垃圾到我覺得特登PO出黎都浪費時間<br />\n不過好多連登仔唔熟一毛招數都係要列出黎"},{"pid":"96957088441963fdb0cbd63668aa12b4120c5897","tid":1321473,"uid":97770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:03:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8eb1aa5fd13d4abcb15fc7eaf27cc5d6493d7ec1","tid":1321473,"uid":105511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:03:31.000Z","msg":"第一句通常都係雖然我都XXXXX 之後就係但係我覺得XXXXX<br />\n係咁講d不切實際 釋出善意 民意 中計 呢d on9野 <br />\n黑警一早俾人灌輸既就係絕對服從上級命令<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">30.警務人員須服從合法命令<br />\n所有警務人員須服從其上級人員以口頭或書面發出的一切合法命令，亦須服從及遵守根據本條例訂立的警察規例及命令。<br />\n34.威脅或侮辱上級或同級的人員<br />\n任何警務人員如威脅或侮辱另一上級或同級的人員，而該人員正在當值，或該項威脅或侮辱是與被如此威脅或侮辱的人員執行職責有關，或因其執行職責而起的，則循簡易程序定罪後，可處罰款$500或監禁1年。</span><br />\n黑警同上級關係等同大陸人同維尼<br />\n用下腦都知前線冇可能會作反啦 唯一反對方法就係辭職<br />\n一堆聖母以為講兩講就可以感化到d黑警<br />\n要辭職一早辭左啦 洗撚等到依家"},{"pid":"9036ffe2a6de30e45df177713bc6606ca5177c9f","tid":1321473,"uid":263423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05350a8fe44390bb70dde72d634cc3036af0ebb9","tid":1321473,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5fcb68a35f72361c95d4f61f48203182da5590eb","tid":1321473,"uid":263423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:27:34.000Z","msg":"竟然，我仲以為有啲曲緊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:28:55.000Z","msg":"無<br />\n我琴日見到不下十個洗地文<br />\n今日7個"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:10:13.000Z","msg":"有啲樓主話佢哋係分化/曲/文宣"},{"pid":"ed3bb1a8b9f2fb7abe303f5f974267316351bcb6","tid":1321473,"uid":105511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:10:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2641b04a9d7c1db5679ed1fe34ba01282c259f20","tid":1321473,"uid":263423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6dce02f568193654c3d19f03f1d10545b6c751c","tid":132